description: This music mix features some of the biggest hits in music history, performed by legendary artists such as Michael Jackson, Beyoncé, Metallica, and many more. The mix spans several decades and genres, showcasing the diverse talents of musicians like Bon Jovi, AC/DC, and Nirvana. Fans of contemporary music will also find plenty to love, with popular hits from artists like Sam Smith, Justin Timberlake, and Lady Gaga making an appearance.
